{"tid":129329,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"三星 Note 7 再戰江湖？傳換電池翻新後於新興國家開賣","createTime":"2017-02-21T13:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T13:57:12.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9681578998e809d13eacbcf01d7d39340f46abbf","tid":129329,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/24111019/shutterstock_477523453-624x416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2F24111019%2Fshutterstock_477523453-624x416.jpg&h=38af766d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三星電子 Galaxy Note 7 因接連發生爆炸起火事件，迫使三星進行召回並停產停售。不過 Note 7 即將再戰江湖？傳出三星計劃將召回的 Note 7 整修後，於印度等新興國家販售。<br />\n<br />\n日本網站 Gadget 通信 21 日轉述南韓媒體韓國經濟新聞的報導指出，據三星關係人士透露，三星回收的 Galaxy Note 7 在更換電池、整修成翻新機（refurbished phone）後，將再度販售。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，三星在因電池問題召回 Note 7 之前賣出 306 萬支，截至目前為止，召回率為 98%，其中 20 萬支用於調查測試爆炸起火原因，而三星計劃將 250 萬支狀態良好的庫存整修之後重新販售。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，三星將 Note 7 爆炸起火的原因定調為「電池缺陷」，因此翻新版 Note 7 電池容量將縮水，將採用 3000~3200mAh 產品（原先為 3500mAh）。<br />\n<br />\n南韓媒體中央日報日文版也於 21 日轉述韓國經濟新聞的報導指出，三星計劃將召回的 Note 7 更換電池、整修成可媲美新機的翻新機後，最快今年 6 月於印度、越南等新興國家販售。<br />\n<br />\n南韓媒體東亞日報曾於去年 9 月 6 日報導，三星無線事業部長高東真於 9 月 2 日舉行的 Note 7 召回相關記者會上表示，「雖沒有時間進行充分檢討，不過可能會販售翻新版 Note 7」。據悉，召回的 Note 7 在經過品質檢查、更換相關零件後，會以低於定價 25~50% 的價格於印度、印尼等新興市場販售。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://technews.tw/2017/02/21/samsung-will-refurbish-note-7-sell-to-india-and-indonesia-etc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2017%2F02%2F21%2Fsamsung-will-refurbish-note-7-sell-to-india-and-indonesia-etc%2F&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlZzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=a259bbc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://technews.tw/2017/02/21/samsung-will-refurbish-note-7-sell-to-india-and-indonesia-etc/</a>"},{"pid":"5f3f9b459cd3428297b68660950695eccf227a27","tid":129329,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"中國呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdcb8da755a0b292a993dd5e7eaa172b240dc973","tid":129329,"uid":46858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:44:55.000Z","msg":"上次爆炸 今次流電"},{"pid":"982e9455a99ac0cb3136974a306087a5c44eca24","tid":129329,"uid":58999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:03:44.000Z","msg":"點解電話既量詞係支"},{"pid":"fe5d75bbe379747d1be8a4d0b23c206b51d9268c","tid":129329,"uid":60137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:32:56.000Z","msg":"生炸蝻亞豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4e7024970fc662c0a10a99eda822c5c4e6ceb4","tid":129329,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解電話既量詞係支</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣用法"},{"pid":"c5b193945f9fe478afa510d65bb94c8627797e91","tid":129329,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed4060665536304ddb4cf7a0d0f5b16021b02ee","tid":129329,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f965683bc78cc93399386570a7a517b6bce5f8ca","tid":129329,"uid":36078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T02:49:05.000Z","msg":"咁既樣都上唔到飛機啦🙈🙈"},{"pid":"3eb455be30c06967b11c1abadcb90ff89018e173","tid":129329,"uid":1822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T03:02:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最新消息：印度唔會賣翻新 Note 7</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><em>&ldquo;The report on Samsung planning to sell refurbished Galaxy Note 7 smartphones in India is incorrect,&rdquo; said a Samsung India s